likes('Ellen', tennis).%Ellen likes tennis.
likes('John', football).%John likes football.
likes('Tom', baseball).%Tom likes baseball.
likes('Tom', swimming).%Tom likes swimming.
likes('Mark', tennis).%Mark likes tennis.
likes('Bill', X):-likes('Tom', X). % Bill likes what Tom likes.
likes('Ellen', reading).%Эллен likes reading.
likes('Mark', computers).%Марк likes computers.
likes('John', badminton).%Джон likes badminton.
likes('Tom', reading).%Эрик likes reading.
typeOfSport('badminton').%badminton - это вид спорта.
typeOfSport('tennis').%tennis - это вид спорта.
typeOfSport('football').%football - это вид спорта.
typeOfSport('бейсбол').%Бейсбол - это вид спорта.
sportsmen(X):-typeOfSport(S),likes(X, S).% sportsmen - это тот, кто likes какой-нибудь вид спорта.
